From b0af20d33f63c74985a6dd98344326e5111b2fea Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mark Harmstone <maharmstone@fb.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Jan 2025 15:02:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] io_uring: add io_uring_cmd_get_async_data helper
Git-commit: b0af20d33f63c74985a6dd98344326e5111b2fea
Patch-mainline: v6.13-rc7
References: bsc#1257958

Add a helper function in include/linux/io_uring/cmd.h to read the
async_data pointer from a struct io_uring_cmd.

Signed-off-by: Mark Harmstone <maharmstone@fb.com>
Signed-off-by: David Sterba <dsterba@suse.com>
Signed-off-by: Gabriel Krisman Bertazi <krisman@suse.de>
---
 include/linux/io_uring/cmd.h |    5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

--- a/include/linux/io_uring/cmd.h
+++ b/include/linux/io_uring/cmd.h
@@ -118,4 +118,9 @@ static inline struct task_struct *io_uri
 	return cmd_to_io_kiocb(cmd)->tctx->task;
 }
 
+static inline struct io_uring_cmd_data *io_uring_cmd_get_async_data(struct io_uring_cmd *cmd)
+{
+	return cmd_to_io_kiocb(cmd)->async_data;
+}
+
 #endif /* _LINUX_IO_URING_CMD_H */
